---
import "../styles/global.css";
import ModalSuscriptionSection from "./ModalSuscriptionSection.astro";
---

<section 
  class="relative bg-black text-white min-h-screen flex items-center"
  style="background-image: url('https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/attachments/gen-images/public/biblical-study-books-and-cross-on-wooden-desk-with-RPJx04UJmMwpyxuvePkt6p1dc5bcqF.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
  
  <!-- Overlay oscuro para mejorar contraste -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="inline-flex mt-40 items-center space-x-2 bg-yellow-400/10 border border-yellow-400/20 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></span>
          <span class="text-yellow-400 text-sm font-medium">Formacion Biblica de Excelencia</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white">
          Formando
          <span class="text-yellow-400">Siervos</span>
          <br />
          para el Ministerio
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          En el Instituto Internacional Bautista Gracia & Verdad, equipamos a hombres y mujeres con conocimiento
          bíblico sólido y herramientas prácticas para el ministerio efectivo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <ModalSuscriptionSection />
        <button class="border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black text-lg px-8 py-4 bg-transparent">
            <a href="#contacto">          Conocer Más
            </a>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center space-x-8 pt-8" id="programas">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400">500+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Graduados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400">25+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Años de Experiencia</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center" >
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400">15+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Paises Alcanzados</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

